page.title: 14The Tournament of 1985
page.content: On the 23rd March,there was a football and netball tournament for small schools. FOOTBALL We won the first few matches, then we lost 0.1 to Trottiscliffe.We could still win the tournament.The last game came,against Plaxtol.At half time it was 0.0 then Alan our left wing shot but hit the post.It was still 0.0 , Shipbourne had won the football cup but with Trottiscliffe. NETBALL The day before a teacher from Plaxtol School had said the netball team wasn't good enough so they were angry and were determined to win.They won the first few matches and if they won the last game they would win the cup.The match was played,Shipbourne got 12 goals. Shipbourne had won the netball cup. David
